high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter between the sinks.
Pick up the bar of soap that's between the sinks.
Turn left and walk over to stand in front of the toilet in front of you so you are standing in front of it looking at it's tank.
Put the bar of soap in the trash to the right of the toilet.
Turn right and walk over to the right sink and stand in front of it.
Pick up the bar of soap in the sink.
Walk over to where you put the first bar of soap.
Put this bar of soap in the toilet as well please.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk straight to the bathroom sinks.
Pick up the soap between both sinks.
Turn around to face the bathroom door, turn right, walk toward the toilet and turn right again to face the toilet.
Place the soap inside the box beside the toilet.
Turn right, walk straight to the wall, turn left to face the bathroom sink.
Pick up the soap inside the the sink.
Turn around to face the bathroom door, turn right, walk straight to the toilet, and turn right to face the toilet.
Place the soap beside the other soap inside the box beside the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place two bars of soap in a box.

high_descs: Turn to the left to face the sink.
Pick the soap up from off of the sink.
Move to the left to face the toilet.
Place the soap in the trash can next to the toilet.
Move to the right to face the sink to the far left.
Pick up the soap from the sink.
Move to the left to face the toilet.
Place the soap in the trash can next to the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place both soaps inside of the trash can next to the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and head to the vanity counter with sinks.
Pick up the bar of soap in between the sinks on top of the vanity.
Turn around, hang a right towards the window and turn right to face the toilet.
Place the bar of soap inside the gray container to the right of the toilet on the tile floor.
Turn right, head to the wall and turn left to face the vanity.
Pick up the bar of soap inside the vanity sink.
Turn around, hang a right towards the window and turn right to face the toilet.
Place the bar of soap on top of another bar of soap inside the gray container to the right of the toilet on the tile floor.
anns.task_desc: Place two bars of soap into a gray container.
